<button id="valider" style="display: none;" >Valider</button>

<div class="echangePop" style="display: none">
    <h4>Choisissez un premier groupe de deux cartes :</h4>
    <div style="display: flex;">
        <div class="grp-1" style="display: flex; margin-right: 30px;">
            <div style="height: 140px; width: 100px; background-color: red; border: 1px solid black; margin-right: 20px;"></div>
